AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000037> "Markers differ between species, and two sets of markers have been described for mice. HSCs are reportedly CD34-positive, CD45-positive, CD48-negative, CD150-positive, CD133-positive, and CD244-negative.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000037> "hematopoietic stem cell")
