# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000158> (club cell)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "DOI:10.1183/09031936.00146609") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "DOI:10.1378/chest.12-2762") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "GOC:tfm") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:28128362") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:29874100") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:7905712") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000158> "A non-mucous, epithelial secretory cell that is part of the tracheobronchial tree. A club cell has short microvilli but no cilia. A club cell is able to multiply and differentiate into ciliated cells to regenerate the bronchiolar epithelium and it also protects the tracheobronchial epithelium.")
