AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000312> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/cl#cellxgene_subset>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000312> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon/core#human_reference_atlas>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000312> "keratinocyte")
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000312> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000237>)
