AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000564> "These cells are CD11b-negative, CD15-positive, CD16-negative, CD49d-positive, CD68-positive, CD35-negative, and fMLP receptor-negative. They are found in the Band 3 fraction.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000564> "neutrophilic promyelocyte")
