# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000770> (band form basophil)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "GOC:add") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "ISBN:0721601464") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:18466030") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "http://www.cap.org") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000770> "A late basophilic metamyelocyte in which the nucleus is in the form of a curved or coiled band, not having acquired the typical multilobar shape of the mature basophil.")
