AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "SANBI:mhl") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000856> "Neuromast hair cell is a hair cell that acts as a sensory receptor of the neuromast; it is morphologically polarized as a result of the relative position of the single kinocilium and the clusters of stereocilia on its apical surface.")
