AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000955> "pre-B-lymphocyte")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000955> "pre-BII cell")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000955> "pre-B-II cell are also reportedly CD19-positive, CD22-positive, CD38-positive, CD45-positive, and CD48-positive.")
