AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "GOC:dsd") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "GOC:tfm") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:18432934") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002046> "A pro-B cell that is CD22-positive, CD34-positive, CD38-positive and TdT-positive (has TdT activity). Pre-BCR is expressed on the cell surface. Cell is CD19-negative, CD20-negative, complement receptor type 2-negative and CD10-low. D-to-J recombination of the heavy chain occurs at this stage.")
