AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002046> "Markers are commonly associated with human cells. These cells are also reportedly CD21-negative. Transcription factors: PU.1-positive, Ikaros-positive, E2A-positive, and PAX5-positive.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002046> "early pro-B cell")
