# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002192> (metamyelocyte)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "GOC:tfm") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "ISBN:0721601464") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metamyelocyte") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002192> "A eosinophil precursor in the granulocytic series, being a cell intermediate in development between a myelocyte and a band form cell. The nucleus becomes indented where the indentation is smaller than half the distance to the farthest nuclear margin; chromatin becomes coarse and clumped; specific granules predominate while primary granules are rare.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002192> <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1980-3228>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002192> "2010-08-30T01:08:15Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
