# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002324> (basal-myoepithelial cell of mammary gland)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "GOC:tfm") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:11250738") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:19022771") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:38059556") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002324> "A myoepithelial cell that is part of a mammary gland and is located in the basal layer. During lactation, a basal-myoepithelial cell of mammary gland contracts under the stimulation of oxytocin. In humans, a basal-myoepithelial cell of mammary gland can be identified by high levels of CD49f and low levels of EpCAM.")
