AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002377> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/cl#cellxgene_subset>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002377> "immature Schwann cell")
