AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002532> "CD16-mDC")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002532> "Normally represent 65-75% of peripheral blood mDCs (human). They are also CD281-positive (TLR1), CD282-positive (TLR2), CD284-positive (TLR4), CD285-positive (TLR5), CD286-positive (TLR6), CD288-positive (TLR8), CD289-positive (TLR9), and CD290-positive (TLR10) by RT-PCR [PMID:17332250]. Upon TLR stimulation, these cells are potent producers of TNF-alpha, while producing little CXCL8 (IL8).")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002532> "CD16-positive myeloid dendritic cell")
EquivalentClasses(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002532> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0000782> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002104> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PR_000001483>) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002215> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0032640>)))
