# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0020017> (M0 macrophage)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "DOI:10.1186/s12885-022-09872-y") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:30861466") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0020017> "A macrophage that has not yet undergone polarization into a specific macrophage subtype. These cells are non-activated and have the potential to differentiate into inflammatory (M1) or alternatively activated (M2) macrophage subtypes in response to appropriate stimuli.")
