AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:32555229") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:33796062") rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033015> "In response to elevated intraocular pressure, a retinal astrocyte may modulate extracellular matrix remodeling. In the human retina, a retinal astrocyte is GFAP-positive, SOD3-positive and GYPC-positive.")
