# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033044> (deuterosomal cell)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:31558434") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:331922198") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:36883528") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:37291214") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033044> "An epithelial cell part of respiratory tract epithelium that is a precursor of a multi-ciliated cell. This cell actively amplifies centrioles, a required step for multiciliogenesis.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033044> <https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6677-8489>)
