AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033044> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon/core#human_reference_atlas>)
AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:31558434") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:331922198") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:36883528") rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033044> "In humans, deuterosomal cells have been noted to have enriched expression of the following: PLK4, FOXJ1, DEUP1, FOXN4, YPEL1, HES6 and CDC20B. Deuterosomal cells were termed after deuterosomes, the platforms of active centriole amplification.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033044> "deuterosomal cell")
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033044> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_0002368>)
