# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033066> (pre-granulosa cell)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:17639032") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:32759216") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:33970370") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:38178246") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033066> "A supporting cell that is part of the ovary and differentiates into a granulosa cell. A pre-granulosa cell develops from an early supporting gonadal cell by repressing testis determination, which can then proliferate to form primordial follicles.")
