# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033087> (placental resident macrophage)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "PMID:39007150") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_4033087> "A tissue-resident macrophage that is part of the placenta. This cell helps preventing immunological rejection of the fetus by modulating the immune environment. A placental resident macrophage has high plasticity to adapt to the changing needs of each phase of pregnancy.")
